        "created_at": "2021-06-24T01:50:53.970Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I think the reason the settings window looks different is because it uses a different method for creating the window than the chat color window. It seems to launch a new signal.exe process when you open it, and the chat color window doesn’t. The settings window also takes a really long time to open.</p>\n<p>I agree they should work on making them more consistent.</p>",
