        "created_at": "2025-11-20T13:16:17.481Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Consistency not only in the use, but also the whole look-and-feel is a basic usability-criteria.</p>\n<p>It’s okay to have differences between platforms, because consistency with the look-and-feel of the platform is more relevant but to be consistent with the other platforms. But inside an app on a platform consistency is crucial for a good usability.</p>",
